PrecisAuthority to enter into the CANADA-NEWFOUNDLAND COOPERATION AGREEMENT FOR FORESTRY DEVELOPMENT 1990-1995 which provides for the implementation of cost-shared programs designed to encourage and support intensive and integrated forest management measures, intensify research, development and technology transfer initiatives and to enhance public awareness of the importance of forest resources.

precis:
Authority to enter into the CANADA-NEWFOUNDLAND COOPERATION AGREEMENT FOR
FORESTRY DEVELOPMENT 1990-1995 which provides for the implementation of
cost-shared programs designed to encourage and support intensive and
integrated forest management measures, intensify research, development
and technology transfer initiatives and to enhance public awareness of the
importance of forest resources.
